Process Engineer - Melting

AK Steel

- Mansfield, OH 44903

PROCESS ENGINEER – MELTING
AK Steel’s Mansfield, OH operation has an immediate need for a Process Engineer - Melting to join our team. The Process Engineer - Melting is accountable for providing full professional engineering expertise in the planning and execution of technical projects within the Melting Department. The ideal candidate must be able to manage several projects and excellent communication and problem solving skills. Our facility is the leading producer of specialty flat rolled stainless steels.
Primary Responsibilities:
Research alternative solutions as they relate to quality, production and cost requirements
Assist in the developing of cost effective solutions to production problems
Develops analysis, prepares and executes technical projects
Works closely with Design Engineering, Operating and Maintenance with engineering applications as they relate to safety, quality, production and cost
Manage several project at a time
Qualifications:
Bachelor Degree in Material Science, Metallurgy or Chemical Engineering degree
Excellent communication and problem solving skills
Extensive computer skills
Why Apply?
Challenging work.
Excellent growth and advancement opportunities.
Bonus program.
Tuition reimbursement.
